$date
  2026-06-07T00:00:00.000Z
$end
$version
  WaveCrux board demo fixture generator
$end
$comment
  Digilent Nexys A7 out-of-box demo — vector buses.
  LED show: cylon / VU bar / chase / switch-mirror / expand / sparkle.
  Seven-seg: decoded readout — counter / accelerometer axes (all digits live). Buttons: staggered presses.
  Re-generate with `dart run tool/generate_board_demo_fixtures.dart`.
$end
$timescale 1 ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 16 ! leds $end
$var wire 16 " sws $end
$var wire 1 # btnC $end
$var wire 1 $ btnU $end
$var wire 1 % btnL $end
$var wire 1 & btnR $end
$var wire 1 ' btnD $end
$var wire 4 ( digit0 $end
$var wire 4 ) digit1 $end
$var wire 4 * digit2 $end
$var wire 4 + digit3 $end
$var wire 4 , digit4 $end
$var wire 4 - digit5 $end
$var wire 4 . digit6 $end
$var wire 4 / digit7 $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
